T1  - A New Algebraic Geometry Algorithm for Integer Programming
AU  - Bertsimas, Dimitris
AU  - Perakis, Georgia
AU  - Tayur, Sridhar
Y1  - 2000/07/01
PY  - 2000
DA  - 2000/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.46.7.999.12033
