T1  - Bounds on the Opportunity Cost of Neglecting Reoptimization in Mathematical Programming
AU  - Oğuz, Osman
Y1  - 2000/07/01
PY  - 2000
DA  - 2000/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.46.7.1009.12041
