JO  - Management Science
SP  - 1009
EP  - 1012
VL  - 46
IS  - 7
PB  - INFORMS
N2  - Postoptimality or sensitivity analysis are well-developed subjects in almost all branches of mathematical programming. In this note, we propose a simple formula which can be used to get preliminary bounds on the value of this type of analysis for a specific class of mathematical programming problems. We also show that our bounds are tight.
AB  - Postoptimality or sensitivity analysis are well-developed subjects in almost all branches of mathematical programming. In this note, we propose a simple formula which can be used to get preliminary bounds on the value of this type of analysis for a specific class of mathematical programming problems. We also show that our bounds are tight.
